      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone looking for reliable transportation. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and have been serviced regularly, there are visible signs of wear and tear on both the exterior paint and the interior upholstery. It has been well-maintained mechanically to ensure it remains roadworthy, though it lacks the cosmetic perfection of a newer model. Expect a solid, functional car that prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
