    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This specimen exhibits a pristine exterior finish and an interior that retains its original showroom integrity. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance. For the discerning collector or enthusiast, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly superlative example of its class, defined by its impeccable provenance and near-flawless preservation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
