    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally babied, garage-kept, and there isn't a single flaw to be found. If you're looking for that 'brand new' experience without the dealership stress, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for you to come by and see just how flawless it is in person!",
      "price": 43500.0,
