    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a factory-correct subframe with documented reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides surgical engagement, feeding power through a perfectly calibrated variable M differential. The exterior retains its original luster with no paint metered outside factory tolerances, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple and free of bolster wear. Mechanically peerless, with a telepathic throttle response and a chassis that remains as rigid as the day it left Regensburg. Full service history included.",
